auto; progress.
rewrite size_pad2blocks //.
inline RaiseFun(BlockSponge.BIRO.IRO).f.
wp; sp.
call (_ : ={BlockSponge.BIRO.IRO.mp}); first sim.
auto.
auto; progress. by rewrite blocks2bits_nil.
